<span class="name"><a name="99281"></a></span><span class="postdetails">#1:&nbsp;<font color=black><b>Ceremonial Elixer of Scholarship (xp modifier quest)</b> Author:&nbsp;<b>Sarc</b>,&nbsp;</font></span><span class="postdetails"><font color=black></font></span>
<a href="viewtopic.php?p=99281#99281"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails"><font color=black>Posted: Wed Mar 16, 2005 12:46 pm</font><span class="gen"><br>
